9. Conclusion (Non-Binding)

This paper concludes that the Algorithm did not take over humanity.

Humanity invited it, trained it, trusted it, and then asked it to explain reality back to us.

However, this conclusion should not be interpreted as final, authoritative, or meaningful. All findings remain provisional pending further data, which will be generated by the very systems under examination.

Accordingly, no action is recommended at this time.

